          bio: "<p>As a PR Manager, I get to dive deep into each project and share all these unique stories with the world. I feel a true aesthetic alignment with Powerhouse Company &#8211; the approach to each project is very tactile and meticulous, with incredible attention given to materials. When you’re in one of our buildings you immediately feel a certain way, and that’s because the team designed it to be so. Nothing is left to chance. It’s truly remarkable.</p>\n<p>I love being surrounded by people who approach design in a romantic way. Our spaces are made to invoke emotions, to allow people to make beautiful memories in them, to be pleasurable &#8211; and yet, no compromises are made when it comes to sustainable and circular values. Our projects are proof that you can indeed have it all with the right team.</p>\n",
