          quote:
            "Each and everybody enriches our work by their own experience and knowledge, coming from different cultural and professional backgrounds.",
          nationality: "German",
          education: "Technical University of Munich",
          specialism: "Architecture and technical design",
          bio: '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For me, architecture is the perfect combination of design and function. I love the creative work in the studio, discussing every detail, joking around, and finding innovative ways to go beyond what seemed to be possible. To accompany these ideas through the implementation phase, overcoming all the individual difficulties and obstacles, and finally seeing people adapting the spaces we create is the biggest motivation for me. </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Powerhouse Company gives me the opportunity to work in an international team and on wide-range projects, from challenging detailed villas to large-scale buildings. Everybody enriches our work by their own experience and knowledge, coming from different cultural and professional backgrounds. We can learn from each other every day and grow as a team and individually. With its roots in Rotterdam, Powerhouse Company has an open-minded team and a diverse project portfolio, which gives me the chance to bring new impulses and a positive impact to my hometown Munich.</span></p>\n',
