          search: false,
          quote: "",
          nationality: "Norwegian",
          education: "Oslo School of Architecture and Design",
          specialism: "",
          bio: "<p>As I have followed the work of Powerhouse Company over the years, I have consistently been fascinated by the elegance and architectural quality in each project, coupled with a thorough contextual adaptation. Currently, as architects, we have a unique opportunity to develop sustainable and future-proof solutions without compromising great design, and I believe Powerhouse Company is successfully achieving this balance.</p>\n<p>I find great satisfaction in collaborating with the diverse range of individuals in the industry, working as a team across disciplines to execute outstanding projects. It&#8217;s rewarding to develop ideas with clients one day and discuss solutions on the building site with contractors or builders the next. The best results emerge when collective intelligence comes into play.</p>\n<p>The most rewarding aspect of my job is the collaborative creation process with the team, turning ideas and designs we believe in into built environments for everyone to enjoy.</p>\n",
