          bio: "<p>The first time I became aware of Powerhouse Company was through the striking design of The Baan Tower. The tower stood proudly in the middle of a black-and-white image, surrounded by a threatening cloudy sky. It’s very exciting to see The Baan Tower now being built with beautiful simplicity.</p>\n<p>To me, that’s what Powerhouse Company represents: designing and realising well-developed and well-thought-out buildings with apparently simple yet uncompromising detailing. I’m very pleased to be able to continue my pursuit of creating beautiful places for everyone to live, create, relax, work, and enjoy their lives.</p>\n",
