          quote:
            "I think that cultural exchange of knowledge, in particular, strengthens us every day and stimulates our creative minds. ",
          nationality: "Italian",
          education: "IUAV University of Venice",
          specialism: "Graphic Design",
          bio: '<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Being the graphic designer of an architectural company means you have to be an all-round designer. The daily tasks can vary from designing a book to creating an exhibition and supporting the architects in their outputs, as well as curating every detail of what we communicate while maintaining the image of the company. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">At Powerhouse Company, I enjoy being surrounded by talented and creative people. I think that cultural exchange of knowledge, in particular, strengthens us every day and stimulates our creative minds. </span></p>\n<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">If I weren’t doing this job, I would probably do a job where you have to create something with your hands; I love handling materials, experimenting, drawing, and crafting.</span></p>\n',
