          specialism: "Communication strategy, PR & media relations",
          bio: "<p>Being part of Powerhouse Company means being part of an international team of passionate and talented creatives. With colleagues from diverse cultural backgrounds, the office buzzes with energy and inspiration, creating a dynamic environment where bold ideas grow. Every day, I enjoy being part of it. </p>\n<p>I love how Powerhouse Company’s projects go beyond mere functionality. Each project is thoughtfully designed with attention given to aesthetics, sustainability, and a deep commitment to improving quality of life. They don’t just shape spaces – they create thriving communities and leave a meaningful mark on the world. Whether it’s a residential development, public space, or cultural building, every project tells a unique story. As PR &#038; Communications Manager, I’m proud to bring these stories to life and share them with the world.</p>\n",
